<HEADLINE> 4 Killed, 30 Injured in Road Mishap in Bangladesh </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Four passengers died on the spot, and the injured were
immediately sent to Sylhet Osmani Medical College Hospital where
five, including a child and a woman, were stated to be "in
critical condition."
</P>
<P>
Sources said the victims came from Comilla district to visit
the tomb of Hazrat Shahjalal, a Muslim saint, and fell into
trouble while returning. 
</P>
</TEXT>
