<HEADLINE> Ghana Urges S. Leone's Rebel to Embrace Peace </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, July 8 (Xinhua) -- Ghanaian President Jerry John
Rawlings has appealed the rebel Revolutionary United Front (RUF)
