that with the reinforcement of troops, the United Nations would
work with the Sierra Leonean government to stabilize the situation
and strengthen governmental machinery.
</P>
<P>
Sierra Leone, which has seen more than eight years of
instability manifested by rebel insurgency, is now faced with
making peace with itself and meeting the desires of its people and
the international community following the recent hostage crisis.
