<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 8 (Xinhua) -- China's top legislator Li Peng said
here today that the National People's Congress (NPC) should
earnestly carry out the directives made recently by Chinese
President Jiang Zemin.
</P>
<P>
Jiang has stressed on many occasions that the Communist Party
of China should always spearhead the development requirements of
China's advanced social productive forces, the progressive course
of China's advanced culture and the fundamental interests of the
Chinese people.
