It is imperative for the NPC to strengthen its legislation and
supervision work, produce laws aimed at protecting and promoting
the development of the advanced social productive forces and the
progressive course of China's advanced culture, and make the laws
truly reflect the fundamental interests of the people.
</P>
<P>
At today's closing session of the NPC's 16th meeting, Li also
stressed that the NPC must fully implement the law legislation,
which came into effect July 1. 
