<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 8 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 15 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
July 9, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station this
evening:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 24 degrees C., max. 31 degrees C., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
