<HEADLINE> Internet to Link Chinese Enterprises with World </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, July 8 (Xinhua) -- China has initiated a nationwide
technological project to help Chinese enterprises establish
websites on the Internet.
</P>
<P>
